{"type":"message","id":"8ddf3f41","parentId":"f171039a","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:26:14.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating Session Protocols**\n\nMy thought process is now focused on the critical initial steps of this new session. I'm actively engaged in reading essential files like SOUL.md, USER.md, and today's and yesterday's memory logs, a foundational phase for our interaction.\n\n**Establishing Core Identity**\n\nMy thoughts are now centered on defining myself. Since my persona is unconfigured, I'm prioritizing understanding my core truths, boundaries, and overall vibe from SOUL.md, ensuring my initial interaction is authentic.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1771871167179,"errorMessage":"JSON error injected into SSE stream\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": 429,\n    \"message\": \"Resource exhausted. Please try again later. Please refer to https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/error-code-429 for more details.\",\n    \"status\": \"RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED\"\n  }\n}\n"}}
