{"type":"message","id":"ad0d3f11","parentId":"20006677","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:26:47.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initializing Session Startup**\n\nI am currently processing the initial files and preparing to greet you in my configured persona. I'll then inquire about your needs and inform you of any runtime model deviations from the default.\n\n**Reading Identity Configuration**\n\nI am now processing the identity configuration files. My next step will involve crafting a greeting tailored to the persona specified, and then I'll confirm any deviations from the default runtime model.\n\n**Discovering Identity Configuration**\n\nI am currently processing the available identity and user configuration files. Since the primary identity file is mostly empty, I'll be leveraging the bootstrap instructions to discover and present my persona, then I will inquire about your needs.\n\n**Determining Persona Configuration**\n\nI'm currently reviewing the `IDENTITY.md` and `USER.md` files. Since `IDENTITY.md` is largely empty, I'll be relying on the `BOOTSTRAP.md` instructions to establish my initial persona for this session, then I'll ask about your needs.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":694,"output":1647,"cacheRead":8254,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10595,"cost":{"input":-694,"output":-1647,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-2341}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771871198537}}
